                                    <h1 id="page-title" class="asset-name entry-title">An Open Letter to Washington, from a GMO Activist</h1>
                                    <p class="entry-author">
                                      <span class="post-footers">Posted by <a href="http://www.realclearscience.com/blog/author/alex-berezow/2013/09/">Alex Berezow</a> at Mon, 23 Sep 2013 06:09:43</span>
